episodes.title: Lawyer Reacts | Chad Daybell Triple Cult Murder Death Penalty Trial  - April 11 (PM)
episodes.description:
Chad Daybell, married to Lori Vallow Daybell who is infamously associated with a "doomsday cult," is undergoing trial. He is accused of plotting alongside his wife to eliminate his first wife, Tammy Daybell, in addition to Lori's two children, Tylee Ryan and Joshua Vallow. Facing several counts, including first-degree murder and conspiracy to commit first-degree murder, Chad Daybell risks receiving the death penalty if found guilty.
